---
// Voice cloning — split copy + voice presets card.
---

<section class="section" id="voice">
  <div class="wrap split">
    <div class="split-copy reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n="voice_eyebrow">Tu voz, en otro idioma</span>
      <h2 class="h-sec" style="margin-top:16px;" data-i18n="voice_title">Soná como vos. En cualquier idioma.</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:16px;" data-i18n="voice_sub">Talkdub no te convierte en un robot. Cloná tu propia voz o elegí una predefinida según el contexto.</p>
      <ul class="feat-list">
        <li><span class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.5 10 17 19 7" /></svg></span><span><span class="ft-t" data-i18n="vf1_t">Clon de tu voz</span><span class="ft-d" data-i18n="vf1_d">Entrenás Talkdub con 30 segundos de tu voz y hablás en inglés o italiano sonando como vos.</span></span></li>
        <li><span class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.5 10 17 19 7" /></svg></span><span><span class="ft-t" data-i18n="vf2_t">Voces predefinidas</span><span class="ft-d" data-i18n="vf2_d">¿No querés clonar? Elegí un tono listo: casual, profesional o de entrevista.</span></span></li>
        <li><span class="tick"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.5 10 17 19 7" /></svg></span><span><span class="ft-t" data-i18n="vf3_t">Tono natural</span><span class="ft-d" data-i18n="vf3_d">Entonación, pausas y ritmo humanos. Nada de cadencia robótica ni metálica.</span></span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="split-media reveal">
      <div class="card card-pad">
        <div class="voice-presets">
          <div class="preset featured">
            <span class="p-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8.5" r="3.8" /><path d="M5 20c.8-3.6 3.5-5.5 7-5.5s6.2 1.9 7 5.5" /></svg></span>
            <div class="p-meta">
              <div class="p-name" data-i18n="preset_yours">Tu voz (clonada)</div>
              <div class="p-desc" data-i18n="preset_yours_d">Tu timbre real en el idioma de destino</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-mini" aria-hidden="true">
              <i style="height:40%"></i><i style="height:70%"></i><i style="height:100%"></i><i style="height:55%"></i><i style="height:85%"></i><i style="height:35%"></i><i style="height:65%"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="tag tgt" data-i18n="preset_active">Activa</span>
          </div>
          <div class="preset">
            <span class="p-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 5l12 7-12 7z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" /></svg></span>
            <div class="p-meta"><div class="p-name" data-i18n="preset_casual_n">Casual</div><div class="p-desc" data-i18n="preset_casual_d">Relajado y cercano, para charlas</div></div>
            <div class="p-mini" aria-hidden="true"><i style="height:30%"></i><i style="height:55%"></i><i style="height:45%"></i><i style="height:70%"></i><i style="height:40%"></i><i style="height:60%"></i><i style="height:35%"></i></div>
          </div>
          <div class="preset">
            <span class="p-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 5l12 7-12 7z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" /></svg></span>
            <div class="p-meta"><div class="p-name" data-i18n="preset_pro_n">Profesional</div><div class="p-desc" data-i18n="preset_pro_d">Claro y neutro, para reuniones</div></div>
            <div class="p-mini" aria-hidden="true"><i style="height:50%"></i><i style="height:60%"></i><i style="height:55%"></i><i style="height:65%"></i><i style="height:50%"></i><i style="height:58%"></i><i style="height:52%"></i></div>
          </div>
          <div class="preset">
            <span class="p-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 5l12 7-12 7z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" /></svg></span>
            <div class="p-meta"><div class="p-name" data-i18n="preset_int_n">Entrevista</div><div class="p-desc" data-i18n="preset_int_d">Seguro y articulado, para cámara</div></div>
            <div class="p-mini" aria-hidden="true"><i style="height:45%"></i><i style="height:80%"></i><i style="height:50%"></i><i style="height:90%"></i><i style="height:55%"></i><i style="height:75%"></i><i style="height:48%"></i></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
